<p>Think about the work that drains your hours. Writing blog posts. Responding to reviews. Posting on social media. Sending follow-up emails. Updating your Google Business Profile. AI handles all of that.</p>
<h3>The Practical Definition</h3>
<p>AI tools take a set of inputs (your business name, your services, your location) and produce useful outputs (blog posts, social media captions, review responses, email sequences). They learn patterns from data and improve over time.</p>
<p>For a local business owner, this means one thing. You get the output of a full marketing team without hiring one.</p>
