<p>AI writes <a href="/blog/email-marketing-local-businesses/">email sequences</a>, personalizes subject lines, and segments audiences based on behavior. A plumber can set up an automated sequence that sends a thank-you email after a service call, requests a review 3 days later, and offers a maintenance discount 30 days after that.</p>
<p>The entire sequence runs without manual effort. AI personalizes each email based on the service performed and the customer history.</p>
